    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '<b><color=#66CC77>1.</color> Show Your Hands</b>

    Hold both hands
    in front of the headset with fingers spread. The cameras need a clear view of
    all fingers.


    <b><color=#66CC77>2.</color> Wait for Detection</b>

    Green
    (left) and blue (right) skeleton overlays will appear on the calibration canvas
    as tracking locks on.


    <b><color=#66CC77>3.</color> Hold Steady</b>

    Once
    both hands reach <b>High Confidence</b>, a 3-second countdown begins. Keep hands
    still until it completes.


    <b><color=#66CC77>4.</color> Automatic Transition</b>

    When
    calibration succeeds, the scene fades smoothly into your rehabilitation session.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
